trans-unit.source: Represents an entry in either back or forward navigation history.
trans-unit.target: 후방 또는 전방 탐색 기록의 항목을 나타냅니다.

trans-unit.source: [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_wpf](~/includes/tlasharptla-wpf-md.md)] implements a navigation history service that stores one entry for each piece of content that has been previously navigated to, just like navigation history in [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_ie](~/includes/tlasharptla-ie-md.md)].
trans-unit.target: [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_wpf](~/includes/tlasharptla-wpf-md.md)] 이전에 탐색, 탐색 기록에서와 마찬가지로 콘텐츠의 각 부분에 대 한 하나의 항목을 저장 하는 탐색 기록 서비스 구현 [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_ie](~/includes/tlasharptla-ie-md.md)]합니다.

trans-unit.source: Navigation history comprises two stacks, one that remembers back navigation history, and one that remembers forward navigation history.
trans-unit.target: 탐색 기록에는 두 스택, 탐색 기록 기억 하 고 다른 하나는 앞으로 탐색 기록 기억 구성 됩니다.

trans-unit.source: An entry for the current item is added to back navigation history when a forward navigation occurs.
trans-unit.target: 현재 항목에 대 한 항목이 후방 앞으로 탐색 발생할 때 탐색 기록에 추가 됩니다.

trans-unit.source: This occurs in the following situations:

The `Navigate` method is called (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigate%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>, <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.Navigate%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.Navigate%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>).

The `GoForward` method is called (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.GoForward%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>, <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.GoForward%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.GoForward%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>).

The forward button on the navigation [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_ui](~/includes/tla2sharptla-ui-md.md)] that is displayed from the current navigator ([!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xbap](~/includes/tla2sharptla-xbap-md.md)], <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame>).
trans-unit.target: 탐색 모음에서 전달 단추 [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_ui](~/includes/tla2sharptla-ui-md.md)] 현재 탐색기에서 표시 되는 ([!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xbap](~/includes/tla2sharptla-xbap-md.md)], <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame>).

trans-unit.source: Likewise, an entry for the current item is added to forward navigation history before a back navigation occurs, which happens when:
trans-unit.target: 뒤로 탐색이 발생 하기 전에 현재 항목에 대 한 항목이 앞으로 탐색 기록에 추가 되는 마찬가지로 때:

trans-unit.source: The `GoBack` method is called (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.GoBack%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>, <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.GoBack%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.GoBack%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>).

The back button on the navigation [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_ui](~/includes/tla2sharptla-ui-md.md)] that is displayed from the current navigator ([!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xbap](~/includes/tla2sharptla-xbap-md.md)], <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame>).
trans-unit.target: 탐색 모음에 뒤로 단추 [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_ui](~/includes/tla2sharptla-ui-md.md)] 현재 탐색기에서 표시 되는 ([!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xbap](~/includes/tla2sharptla-xbap-md.md)], <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame>).

trans-unit.source: Each entry in back and forward navigation history is an instance of the <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.JournalEntry> class.
trans-unit.target: 각 항목 뒤에 앞으로 탐색 기록의 인스턴스가 <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.JournalEntry> 클래스입니다.

trans-unit.source: Each <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.JournalEntry> object encapsulates information about a particular navigation, including a name for the entry (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.JournalEntry.Name%2A>), whether the entry is kept alive (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.JournalEntry.KeepAlive%2A>) and the [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_uri](~/includes/tlasharptla-uri-md.md)] for the content that is navigated to (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.JournalEntry.Source%2A>).
trans-unit.target: 각 <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.JournalEntry> 항목에 대 한 이름을 포함 하 여 특정 탐색에 대 한 정보를 캡슐화 하는 개체 (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.JournalEntry.Name%2A>) 항목은 활성 상태로 유지 여부에 관계 없이 (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.JournalEntry.KeepAlive%2A>) 및 [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_uri](~/includes/tlasharptla-uri-md.md)] 를 탐색 하는 콘텐츠에 대 한 (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.JournalEntry.Source%2A>).

trans-unit.source: You can retrieve all the <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.JournalEntry> objects in back navigation history by enumerating the <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.BackStack%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> or <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.BackStack%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> properties.
trans-unit.target: 모든를 검색할 수 있습니다는 <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.JournalEntry> 열거 하 여 탐색 기록 개체 뒤에 <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.BackStack%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> 또는 <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.BackStack%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> 속성입니다.

trans-unit.source: For forward navigation history, you can retrieve all the <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.JournalEntry> objects by enumerating the <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.ForwardStack%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> or <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.ForwardStack%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> properties.
trans-unit.target: 앞으로 탐색 기록에 대 한 모든 검색할 수 있습니다는 <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.JournalEntry> 열거 하 여 개체는 <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.ForwardStack%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> 또는 <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.ForwardStack%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> 속성입니다.

trans-unit.source: If you need to remove the most recent <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.JournalEntry> object from back navigation history, to prevent navigation to it, for example, you can call the `RemoveBackEntry` method (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.RemoveBackEntry%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>, <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.RemoveBackEntry%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.RemoveBackEntry%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>), which removes the <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.JournalEntry> object and returns a reference to it.
trans-unit.target: 가장 최근의 제거 해야 할 경우 <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.JournalEntry> 개체를 탐색 등을 방지 하기 위해 뒤로 탐색 기록에서 호출할 수 있습니다는 `RemoveBackEntry` 메서드 (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.RemoveBackEntry%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>, <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.RemoveBackEntry%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.RemoveBackEntry%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>)를 제거 하는 <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.JournalEntry> 개체 및에 대 한 참조를 반환 합니다.

trans-unit.source: You cannot add <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.JournalEntry> objects to navigation history, however, because you can neither instantiate nor derive from <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.JournalEntry>, and because no type implements a member to do so.
trans-unit.target: 하지만 추가할 수 없습니다 <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.JournalEntry> 개체를 탐색 기록 인스턴스화할 아니고에서 파생 될 수 있으므로 <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.JournalEntry>, 때문이 이렇게 하려면 멤버를 구현 하는 형식이 없습니다.

trans-unit.source: However, you can add custom <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.CustomContentState> objects to back navigation history by calling the `AddBackEntry` method (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.AddBackEntry%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.AddBackEntry%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.AddBackEntry%2A>); <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService> adds the <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.CustomContentState> object to an internally-created <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.JournalEntry> object, which is then added to the back navigation history.
trans-unit.target: 그러나 사용자 지정을 추가할 수 <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.CustomContentState> 개체를 호출 하 여 탐색 기록을 다시는 `AddBackEntry` 메서드 (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.AddBackEntry%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.AddBackEntry%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.AddBackEntry%2A>); <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService> 추가 <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.CustomContentState> 개체는 내부적으로 생성 <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.JournalEntry> 개체를 뒤로 탐색 기록에 추가 됩니다.

trans-unit.source: The following example shows how to retrieve the most recent <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.JournalEntry> object from the back navigation stack to get the <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.JournalEntry.Name%2A> and <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.JournalEntry.Source%2A> property values.
trans-unit.target: 다음 예제에서는 가장 최근에 검색 하는 방법을 보여 줍니다 <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.JournalEntry> 가져오려는 뒤로 탐색 스택에서 개체는 <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.JournalEntry.Name%2A> 및 <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.JournalEntry.Source%2A> 속성 값입니다.

trans-unit.target: 의해 호스팅되는 콘텐츠 <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame>, 또는 [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_ie7](~/includes/tla2sharptla-ie7-md.md)], 탐색을 표시 [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_ui](~/includes/tla2sharptla-ui-md.md)] 사용자가를 뒤로 및 앞으로 탐색 기록을 탐색할 수 있도록 합니다.
